      <title>菲律宾抗议者践踏习近平肖像，谴责中国海上“侵略”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-protesters-trample-xi-effigy-condemn-chinas-maritime-aggression-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，马尼拉的抗议者践踏中国国家主席习近平的肖像，谴责中国在南海“侵略”菲律宾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-protesters-trample-xi-effigy-condemn-chinas-maritime-aggression-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 06:23:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚报告限制社交媒体内容的请求增加</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/malaysia-reports-increase-requests-restrict-social-media-content-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚周二表示，敦促 Facebook 运营商 Meta 和短视频服务 TikTok 加强对其平台的监控，政府报告今年有害社交媒体内容急剧增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/malaysia-reports-increase-requests-restrict-social-media-content-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 06:09:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国将在人工智能领域投资 70 亿美元，以保持芯片优势</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/south-korea-invest-7-bln-ai-bid-retain-edge-chips-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈周二表示，韩国将在 2027 年之前在人工智能领域投资 9.4 万亿韩元（69.4 亿美元），作为保持尖端半导体芯片全球领先地位的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/south-korea-invest-7-bln-ai-bid-retain-edge-chips-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 05:34:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梵蒂冈外长对越南进行史无前例的访问</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/vatican-foreign-minister-travels-vietnam-unprecedented-visit-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[梵蒂冈外交部长保罗·理查德·加拉格尔周二开始对共产党统治的越南进行史无前例的为期六天的访问，双方致力于建立更密切的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/vatican-foreign-minister-travels-vietnam-unprecedented-visit-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 05:27:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾军演模拟击退中国演习演变成攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-war-games-simulate-repelling-chinese-drill-that-turns-into-attack-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾国防部周二表示，今年台湾的年度军演将在海上进行“杀伤区”演习，以打破封锁，并模拟中国突然将其环岛常规演习转变为实际攻击的场景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-war-games-simulate-repelling-chinese-drill-that-turns-into-attack-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 05:14:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>充满选举的 2024 年将如何影响世界市场</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-election-pix-graphic-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在充满选举的一年里，市场迄今为止对选举结果不屑一顾，焦点完全集中在一场可能对从国际贸易到新兴市场债务等方方面面产生影响的竞赛上：11 月的美国总统竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-election-pix-graphic-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 05:07:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯南部洪水袭击数千人面临危险</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/thousands-people-risk-floods-hit-russias-south-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯官方通讯社周二称，洪水正在威胁俄罗斯南部库尔干地区，导致超过 19,000 人面临生命危险。几天前，前所未有的洪水导致数千人流离失所，并淹没了乌拉尔地区的一座城市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/thousands-people-risk-floods-hit-russias-south-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 04:55:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行因出售阿根廷业务而录得10亿美元税前损失</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/hsbc-sell-argentina-business-galicia-550-mln-deal-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰控股周二表示，随着该银行加大对亚洲的关注，将出售其阿根廷业务，并在 2024 财年第一季度因撤资而录得 10 亿美元的税前损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/hsbc-sell-argentina-business-galicia-550-mln-deal-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 04:25:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国总理表示缅甸对话中涉及的敏感问题必须解决各方</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-remains-neutral-myanmar-conflict-says-foreign-minister-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国总理斯雷塔·塔维信(Srettha Thavisin)在讨论邻国不断升级的冲突的内阁会议后表示，启动缅甸军政府和反军政府组织之间的谈判存在敏感问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-remains-neutral-myanmar-conflict-says-foreign-minister-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 03:27:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雪佛龙将缅甸天然气田股份交给军政府和泰国PTTEP</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chevron-hands-myanmar-gas-field-stake-junta-thailands-pttep-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国能源公司雪佛龙发言人周一表示，该公司已退出缅甸亚达纳天然气田，两年多前该公司谴责了那里的暴力和侵犯人权行为并宣布将退出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chevron-hands-myanmar-gas-field-stake-junta-thailands-pttep-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 02:23:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
